<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vibe Express | Premium API Backend</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        .glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px border rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#050505] text-slate-300 min-h-screen selection:bg-indigo-500/30">
    <div class="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-[10%] -left-[10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-[10%] -right-[10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <nav class="relative z-50 border-b border-white/5 py-4 px-8 flex justify-between items-center backdrop-blur-md">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white uppercase">VibeExpress</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-8">
            <a href="/api/docs" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-all uppercase tracking-widest">API Docs</a>
            <a href="https://github.com" class="px-5 py-2 bg-white text-black rounded-xl font-bold text-sm shadow-xl shadow-white/5 hover:scale-105 transition-all">Github</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-12 mb-32">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400">Node JS 22 &bull; Express 5 Ready</span>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter leading-[0.95]">
                ARCHITECTURE FOR <br>
                <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 via-purple-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">SCALE</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                Elevate your backend development with our production-grade Express.js boilerplate. 
                Built with security, observability, and pure performance as core principles.
            </p>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <a href="/api/docs" class="px-10 py-5 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-[2rem] font-black text-lg tracking-tight shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-500/20 hover:scale-105 transition-all active:scale-95">
                    Interactive API Docs
                </a>
                <button class="px-10 py-5 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] text-white font-black text-lg tracking-tight hover:bg-white/10 transition-all active:scale-95">
                    Source Code
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[3rem] group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-500 mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">Enterprise Security</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium">JWT, Helmet, and CORS policy pre-configured for bulletproof applications.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[3rem] group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-500 mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h4l2 2h4a2 2 0 012 2v1m-6 9a2 2 0 01-2-2v-3.344a1 1 0 01.12-.47l.29-.58a1 1 0 00.12-.47V9.24" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">Smart Logger</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Winston and Morgan integrated for deep observability and effortless debugging.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[3rem] group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-pink-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-pink-500 mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">OpenAPI/Swagger</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Automated documentation generated on-the-fly for your entire API surface.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="mt-40 pt-20 border-t border-white/5 text-center">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
                Powered by Vibe Coding Platform &bull; Node Express Blueprint
            </p>
        </footer>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
